deck: American comedian, actor and voice actor.
description:
Biography

Gilbert Gottfried is a comedian and actor most known for his unique voice.

He is probably best known for being the voice of Iago the parrot in Disney's Aladdin series.

Gilbert also wrote an issue of The Adventures of Superboy.

Comic Related Roles

Gilbert played Nick Knack, a character similar to Toyman, on the Superboy live action show.

Gilbert provided the voice of Mr. Mxyzptlk in Superman: The Animated Series.
